SYNOPSIS: Instructor Sara Ivanhoe leads viewers through a 20-minute yoga routine that offers a body-sculpting workout for even the busiest of schedules. This volume focuses on yoga poses that promote weight loss by raising heart rate, burning fat and calories, strengthening muscles, increasing energy, and improving flexibility. Suitable for all fitness levels, Sara's exercises are both safe and challenging enough for beginners and experts alike.
